o the intimacy and sense of close invoivement, which is"},{"type":"text","text":"the recital's particular charm."},{"type":"entry","text":"retrospect","headword":"retrospect"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 回顾(a review of or meditation on past events) v [回顾(to refer back); 回想(to"},{"type":"text","text":"['retraspekt]"},{"type":"text","text":"go back over in thought)"},{"type":"text","text":"inretrospect回顾，回想"},{"type":"text","text":"reconsideration, reexamination, retrospection"},{"type":"entry","text":"veil","headword":"veil"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.面纱；遮蔽物 v以面纱掩盖(to cover, obscure,or conceal with a veil)"},{"type":"text","text":"[verl]"},{"type":"entry","text":"sharpen","headword":"sharpen"},{"type":"text","text":"inferior"},{"type":"text","text":"['fa:rpan]"},{"type":"entry","text":"hone","headword":"hone"},{"type":"entry","text":"brutality","headword":"brutality"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 野密(the quality or state of being brutal); 暴行(a brutal act or course of action)"},{"type":"text","text":"[bru:'taelati]"},{"type":"entry","text":"frivolity","headword":"frivolity"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.轻浮的行为（a frivolous act or thing）"},{"type":"text","text":"[frr'va:lati]"},{"type":"text","text":"Despite an affected nonchalance which convinced casual observers that he"},{"type":"text","text":"was indifferent about his painting and enjoyed only frivolty, Warhol cared deeply"},{"type":"text","text":"about his art and labored at it diligently."},{"type":"entry","text":"iconoclasm","headword":"iconoclasm"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.破坏偶像的理论，打破旧习（the doctrine,practice,or attitude of an iconoclast)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ar'ka:naklaezam]"},{"type":"entry","text":"texture","headword":"texture"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 质地(identifying quality) ; 结构(overall structure)"},{"type":"text","text":"['tekstfar]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：text（编织）+ure→质地"}]},{"number":241,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"assure","headword":"assure"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 保证(to tell sb. positively);使确信(to convince)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'fur]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：as（一再）+sure（肯定）→一再肯定→使确信"},{"type":"entry","text":"justifiable","headword":"justifiable"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 有理由的，无可非议的(capable of being justified or defended as correct)"},{"type":"text","text":"['dsastrfarabl]"},{"type":"text","text":"图来自justify（v证明是正当或合理的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"vigilance","headword":"vigilance"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 警惕，警觉(the quality or state of being vigilant)"},{"type":"text","text":"[vidsrlans]"},{"type":"text","text":"alertness, watchfulness"},{"type":"entry","text":"frugality","headword":"frugality"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 朴素;节俭(prudence in avoiding waste)"},{"type":"text","text":"[fru'galati]"},{"type":"text","text":"Her frugality should not be confused with miserliness; as long as I have known"},{"type":"text","text":"her, she has always been willing to assist those who are in need."},{"type":"text","text":"economy, thritiness"},{"type":"entry","text":"obstacle","headword":"obstacle"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.障碍，妨碍物"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：ob（反）+sta（站）+（a)cle（表东西）→反着站，挡住了去路→障碍"},{"type":"text","text":"[a:bstakl]"},{"type":"text","text":"obstacle to（doing)sth.（做）某事的障碍"},{"type":"text","text":"hurdlle, impediment, obstruction, snag"},{"type":"entry","text":"trait","headword":"trait"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. (人的)显著特性(a distinguishing feature, as of a person’s character)"},{"type":"text","text":"[trert]"},{"type":"text","text":"attribute, characteristic, peculiarity"},{"type":"entry","text":"sport","headword":"sport"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.炫羅，卖弄(to display or wear ostentatiously)"},{"type":"text","text":"[spo:rt]"},{"type":"text","text":"sportabeard故意蓄着大胡子"},{"type":"entry","text":"concentration","headword":"concentration"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.专心，专注(the act or process of concentrating);集中"},{"type":"text","text":"[ka:nsn'trer{n]"},{"type":"text","t