h little money or food);存在(existence)"}]},{"number":243,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"digression","headword":"digression"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 离题，题外话(an act of turning aside from the main subject or talk about sth."},{"type":"text","text":"[dar'grefn]"},{"type":"text","text":"else)"},{"type":"entry","text":"stinginess","headword":"stinginess"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.小气"},{"type":"text","text":"['stind3inas]"},{"type":"text","text":"圆来自stingy(adj吝啬的)"},{"type":"entry","text":"authorization","headword":"authorization"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.授权，认可（action of authorizing)"},{"type":"text","text":"[:0ara'zetfn]"},{"type":"text","text":"圆来自authorize（v授权，认可）"},{"type":"entry","text":"phony","headword":"phony"},{"type":"text","text":"adlj.假的，欺骗的(not genuine or real)"},{"type":"text","text":"['fauni]"},{"type":"text","text":"false, sham"},{"type":"entry","text":"commit","headword":"commit"},{"type":"definition","text":"v托付(to consign);承诺(to bind or obligate);犯罪(to perpetrate)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ka'mrt]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：com（共同）+mit（送）→一起送给→托付"},{"type":"text","text":"commitment（n.承诺，许诺）"},{"type":"entry","text":"expend","headword":"expend"},{"type":"definition","text":"v花费(to pay out; spend);用光(to use up)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rk'spend]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：ex（出）+pend（支付）→花费"},{"type":"entry","text":"ruminate","headword":"ruminate"},{"type":"text","text":"['ru:minert]"},{"type":"text","text":"cogitate, contemplate, deliberate, ponder"},{"type":"text","text":"rumination（n.沉思：认真考虑）"},{"type":"entry","text":"objection","headword":"objection"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.厌恶，反对(dislike or disapproval)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ab'dzek{n]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：ob（反）+ject（扔）+ion→反过来扔→厌恶，反对"},{"type":"text","text":"Since the author frequently attacks other scholars, his objection to disputes is"},{"type":"text","text":"not only irrelevant but also surprising."},{"type":"entry","text":"incur","headword":"incur"},{"type":"text","text":".招荐(to bring upon oneself)"},{"type":"text","text":"[nn'k3:r]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：in（进入）+cur（跑）→跑进来→招葱"},{"type":"text","text":"Lizzie was a brave woman who could dare to incur a great danger for an"},{"type":"text","text":"adequate object."},{"type":"entry","text":"mechanism","headword":"mechanism"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.结构，机制"},{"type":"text","text":"['mekanrzam]"},{"type":"text","text":"mechanism for resolving the conflict 解决冲突的机制"}]},{"number":244,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 20 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"illiberal","headword":"illiberal"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj偏执的，思想狭隘的(intolerant,bigoted)"},{"type":"text","text":"[r'libaral]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：il（不）+liberal（开明的）→不开明的→偏执的"},{"type":"entry","text":"reminder","headword":"reminder"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.提醒物，纪念品(sth. that makes one remember)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rr'maindar]"},{"type":"text","text":"图来自动词remind（v提醒）：注意不要与remainder（n.剩余物）混淆滑"},{"type":"text","text":"Charlotte Salomon's biography is a reminder that the currents of private life,"},{"type":"text","text":"however diverted, dislodged, or twisted by overpowering public events, retain"},{"type":"text","text":"their hold on the individual recording them."},{"type":"text","text":"inherit"},{"type":"entry","text":"inherit","headword":"inherit"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.继承(to receive property)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rn'herrt]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：in（进入）+herit（继承人）→继承"},{"type":"entry","text":"gawky","headword":"gawky"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj迟钝的，笨拙的（awkward)"},{"type":"text","text":"['go:ki]"},{"type":"text","text":"圆来自gawk（v呆头呆脑地盯着）"},{"type":"text","text":"gawkiness (n.笨拙）"},{"type":"entry","text":"illustrate","headword":"illustrate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.举例说明，用图表等说明（to explain by examples"},{"type":"text","text":"['rlastrert]"},{"type":"text","text":"diagrams, pictures); (解明(to make clear)"},{"type":"text","text":"用图来"},{"type":"text","text":"illustrate"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：i（向内）+lustr（照亮，光）+ate→向内给光明→"},{"type":"text","text":"表示"},{"type":"text","text":"阐明"},{"type":"text","text":"Numerous historical examples illustrate both the"},{"type":"text","text":"overriding influence that scientists’ prejudices have"},{"type":"text","text":"on their interpretation of data and the consequent"},{"type":"text","text":"impairment of their intellectual objectivity."},{"type":"entry","text":"woe","headword":"woe"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 悲痛, 悲衰(a condition of deep suffering from misfortune, affliction, or grief);"},{"type":"text","text":"[wau]"},{"type":"text","text":"不幸，灾难（calamity，misfortune）"},{"type":"entry","text":"flinch","headword":"flinch"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.畏缩，退缩(to draw back; wince;cower)"},{"type":"text","text":"[flInt]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆联想记忆：f(（看作fly，飞）+inch（寸）→一寸一寸向后飞→退缩"},{"type":"text","text":"unflinching（adj.坚定的：不畏缩的)"},{"type":"entry","text":"detest","headword":"detest"},{"type":"definition","text":"v 厌恶，增很(to dislike intensely; hate; abhor)"},{"type":"text","text":"[dr'test]"},{"type":"note","text":"园联想记忆：de+test（测试）→有的学生十分憎恶测试→厌恶"},{"type":"text","text":"图 detestation (n.增恶)"},{"type":"entry","text":"relent","headword":"relent"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.变温和，变宽厚（to become compassionate or forgiving）：减弱（to soften;"},{"type":"text","text":"[rr'lent]"},{"type":"text","text":"mollify)"},{"type":"text","text":"圈词根记忆：re（一再）+lent（松）→（心肠）一再松→变温和，变宽厚"},{"type":"text","text":"unrelenting（adj.持续的；不缓和的；不留情的）"}]},{"number":245,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"self-righteousness","headword":"self-righteousness"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.自以为是"},{"type":"text","text":"[,selfrartfasnas]"},{"type":"text","text":"The action and characters in a melodrama can be so immediately classified"},{"type":"text","text":"that all observers can hiss the villain with an air of smug but enjoyable self-"},{"type":"text","text":"righteousness."},{"type":"text","text":"self-righteous （adj自以为是的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"convulse","headword":"convulse"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 使剧烈震动;震撼(to shake or disturb violently;agitate)"},{"type":"text","text":"[kan'vAls]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：con（强调）+vuls（收缩）+e→不断收缩→使剧烈震动"},{"type":"text","text":"图convulsion（n.疼李；骚动）"},{"type":"entry","text":"affirmation","headword":"affirmation"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 肯定; 断言(the act of affirming or the state of being affirmed; assertion)"},{"type":"text","text":"[aefar'merfn]"},{"type":"text","text":"affirmative （adj. 肯定的;同意的)"},{"type":"entry","text":"churl","headword":"churl"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 粗郡之人(a surly, ill-bred person)"},{"type":"text","text":"[tf3:rl]"},{"type":"note","text":"图联想记忆：粗都之人（churl）不宜进教堂（church）"},{"type":"text","text":"churlish（adj.粗鲁无礼的；脾气坏的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"anatomical","headword":"anatomical"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 解部学的(of, or relating to anatomy)"},{"type":"text","text":"[aena'ta:mrkl]"},{"type":"text","text":"来自anatomy（n.解剖学，解剖）：ana（分开）+tomy（切）→切开→解剖"},{"type":"entry","text":"ramble","headword":"ramble"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 漫步(a leisurely excursion for pleasure) v. 漫步(to move aimlessly from place"},{"type":"text","text":"['raembl]"},{"type":"text","text":"to place)"},{"type":"note","text":"图联想记忆：r+amble（缓行，漫步）→漫步"},{"type":"text","text":"rambling（adj.长而含期的：不切题的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"cloy","headword":"cloy"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. (吃甜食）生腻，吃腻(to surfeit by too much of sth. sweet)"},{"type":"text","text":"[kli]"},{"type":"text","text":"satiate"},{"type":"text","text":"cloying （adj.令人腻烦的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"forbear","headword":"forbear"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 克制(to hold oneself back from especially with an effort);忍耐(to control"},{"type":"text","text":"[fo:r'ber]"},{"type":"text","text":"oneself when provoked)"},{"type":"text","text":"forbearance（n.忍耐，克制）"},{"type":"entry","text":"extract","headword":"extract"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 拔出(to take sth. out with effort or by force);: 强家(to forcefully obtain money or"},{"type":"text","text":"[rk'straekt]"},{"type":"text","text":"information)"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：ex（出）+tract（拉）→拉出→拔出"},{"type":"text","text":"extraction（n.提取；拔出）"},{"type":"entry","text":"abstinent","headword":"abstinent"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.饮食有度的，有节制的，禁欲的（constraining from indulgence of an appetite"},{"type":"text","text":"['ebstinant]"},{"type":"text","text":"or craving or from eating some foods)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：abs（脱离）+tin（拿住）+ent→把握自己脱离某物→禁欲的"},{"type":"text","text":"abstinence（n.节制：蒙欲）"},{"type":"entry","text":"culpable","headword":"culpable"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 有罪的，该受键责的(deserving blame; blameworthy)"},{"type":"text","text":"['kAlpabl]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：culp（罪行）+able→有罪的"},{"type":"text","text":"图culpability（n.有罪；应受指责）"},{"type":"entry","text":"devotional","headword":"devotional"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj 献身的，虚诚的(used in religious worship)"},{"type":"text","text":"[dr'vaufanl]"},{"type":"text","text":"来自devotion（n.献身）"},{"type":"text","text":"devoted（adj.挚爱的：忠诚的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"assemble","headword":"assemble"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.集合，聚集(to collect)：装配，组装(to fit together the parts)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'sembl]"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：as（加强）+semble（类似）→物以类聚→集合"}]},{"number":246,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 20 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"contrive","headword":"contrive"},{"type":"definition","text":"v 计划,设计(to think up; devise; scheme)"},{"type":"text","text":"[kan'trarv]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：contri（反）+ve（看作ven，走）→（和普通人）反着走→设计（新东西）→计"},{"type":"text","text":"划，设计"},{"type":"text","text":"connive, intrigue, machinate, plot"},{"type":"text","text":"contrived （adj.预谋的：人为的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"assiduous","headword":"assiduous"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 勤勉的(diligent, persevering);专心的(attentive)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'sidzuas]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：as（去）+sid（坐）+uous→坐得久的→勤勉的"},{"type":"text","text":"图be assiduous in ...专心于.."},{"type":"text","text":"assiduousness（n.勤奋：勤勉）"},{"type":"entry","text":"daunt","headword":"daunt"},{"type":"text","text":"使胆怯，使畏缩(to dishearten;dismay)"},{"type":"text","text":"[do:nt]"},{"type":"note","text":"图联想记忆：d（看作devil，魔鬼）+aunt（姑姑）→姑姑被魔鬼吓到了→使胆怯"},{"type":"text","text":"daunting（adj.使人畏惧的，令人胆怯的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"boisterous","headword":"boisterous"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 喧闹的(noisy and unruly); 猛烈的(violent)"},{"type":"text","text":"[borstaras]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：boister（喧闹）+ous→喧闹的"},{"type":"text","text":"disorderly, rambunctious, tumultuous, turbulent"},{"type":"text","text":"boisterousness（n.喧闹，欢腾）"},{"type":"entry","text":"quack","headword":"quack"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.冒牌医生，庸医（a pretender to medical skill) adj庸医的"},{"type":"text","text":"[kwak]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：和quick（adj快的）一起记：庸医骗完钱很快消失"},{"type":"text","text":"The popularity of pseudoscience and quack medicines in the nineteenth"},{"type":"text","text":"century suggests that people were very credulous, but the gullibility of the public"},{"type":"text","text":"today makes citizens of yesterday look like hard-nosed skeptics."},{"type":"text","text":"quackery（n.江湖医术：庸医行径）"},{"type":"entry","text":"connoisseur","headword":"connoisseur"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 鉴贯家, 行家(a person who has expert knowledge and keen discrimination in"},{"type":"text","text":"[ka:na's3:r]"},{"type":"text","text":"some field in the fine arts or in matters of taste)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：con（强调）+nois（知道）+s+eur（人）→什么都知道的人→行家"},{"type":"text","text":"connoisseurship（n.鉴赏能力）"},{"type":"entry","text":"abominate","headword":"abominate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 痛恨; 厌恶(to feel hatred and disgust for; loathe)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'ba:minert]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：ab（脱离）+om（看作hom，人）+in+ate→脱离人的模样→痛恨；厌恶"},{"type":"text","text":"abomination（n.令人憎恨的事物：可恶的东西）"},{"type":"entry","text":"derogate","headword":"derogate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.贬低，诽谤(to lower in esteem; disparage)"},{"type":"text","text":"['deragert]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：de（坏）+rog（问，说）+ate→说坏话→贬低"},{"type":"text","text":"derogation（n.含有贬义的言辞）"},{"type":"entry","text":"exculpate","headword":"exculpate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.开脱(to free from blame）;申明无罪，证明无罪(to declare or prove guiltless)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ekskAlpert]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：ex（出）+culp（错，罪）+ate→从罪中解脱→开脱"}]},{"number":247,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<<GRE词汇精选乱序版"},{"type":"entry","text":"befuddle","headword":"befuddle"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.使迷感不解：使酒醉昏迷(to confuse; muddle or stupefy with or as if with drink)"},{"type":"text","text":"[bx'fAdl]"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：be（使）+fuddle（迷糊）→使迷惑不解"},{"type":"text","text":"befuddlement(n.迷感；期涂）"},{"type":"entry","text":"incinerate","headword":"incinerate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.焚化，焚毁(to burn to ashes;cremate)"},{"type":"text","text":"[in'sinarert]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：in（使）+ciner（灰）+ate→使成灰→赞化"},{"type":"text","text":"incinerator（n.（垃圾）荧化炉）"},{"type":"entry","text":"encomiast","headword":"encomiast"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 赞美者(a person who delivers or writes an encomium; a eulogist)"},{"type":"text","text":"[en'kaumiaest]"},{"type":"note","text":"园联想记忆：en+com（看作come）+iast→有目的而来的人→赞美者"},{"type":"text","text":"encomium (n.领词)"},{"type":"entry","text":"choreographic","headword":"choreographic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj舞蹈术的，舞台舞蹈的"},{"type":"text","text":"[,ko:ria'graefik]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自choreography（n.编舞设计，舞蹈设计）"},{"type":"entry","text":"fulminate","headword":"fulminate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v猛烈坪击，严厉遣责（to shoutforth denunciations）"},{"type":"text","text":"['fulmxnert]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：fulmin（雷声）+ate→如雷声般叫喊→严厉谴责"},{"type":"text","text":"图fulmination（n.严厉责：爆发）"},{"type":"entry","text":"polemic","headword":"polemic"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.争论，论战(an aggressive attack or refutation)"},{"type":"text","text":"[pa'lemrk]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：polem（战争）+ic→争论，论战"},{"type":"text","text":"polemically （adv.有争议地)"},{"type":"entry","text":"demarcate","headword":"demarcate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 划分，划界(to mark the limits; to mark the difference between)"},{"type":"text","text":"[di:ma:rkert]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：de（表强调）+marc（看作mark，标记）+ate→做标记→划分，划界"},{"type":"text","text":"demarcation (n.划分)"},{"type":"entry","text":"indulgent","headword":"indulgent"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 放纵的, 纵容的(indulging or characterized by indulgence)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rn'daldzant]"},{"type":"text","text":"图indulgent parents 纵容子女的父母"},{"type":"text","text":"indulgence (n.沉滑；放纵）"},{"type":"entry","text":"plagiarize","headword":"plagiarize"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 型切)，抄袭(to take(sb. else’s ideas, words. etc) and use them as if they were"},{"type":"text","text":"['plerdzara1z]"},{"type":"text","text":"one's own)"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：plagi（斜的）+ar+ize→做歪事→剩窃，抄袭"},{"type":"text","text":"plagiarism(n.窃：抄袭）"},{"type":"entry","text":"etymology","headword":"etymology"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 语源学(the branch of linguistics dealing with word origin and development)"},{"type":"text","text":"[etr'ma:lad3i]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自etymon（n.词源，字根）"},{"type":"text","text":"etymological(adj.词源的;词源学的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"infringe","headword":"infringe"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.违反，侵害(to break a law; violate; trespass)"},{"type":"text","text":"[n'frind3]"},{"type":"text","text":"pensive"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：in（使）+fring（破坏）+e→违反"},{"type":"text","text":"圆infringement (n.侵犯，侵害)"}]},{"number":248,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 20 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"aspire","headword":"aspire"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 渴望，追求，向往(to direct one's hopes and efforts to some important aims)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'sparar]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：a（去）+spir（呼吸）+e→因为太渴望得到，所以不停地呼吸→向往"},{"type":"text","text":"aspiration(n.抱负，渴望）;aspiring（adj.有抱负的，有理想的)"},{"type":"entry","text":"fanatic","headword":"fanatic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.狂热的，盲信的(marked by excessive enthusiasm and often intense"},{"type":"text","text":"[fa'naetrk]"},{"type":"text","text":"uncritical devotion) n. 狂热者(a person marked or motivated by an extreme,"},{"type":"text","text":"unreasoning enthusiasm)"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自fan（n.入迷者）"},{"type":"text","text":"fanatical (adj狂热的;入迷的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"patriot","headword":"patriot"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 爱国者，爱国主义者(one who loves his/her country and supports its authority"},{"type":"text","text":"['pertriat]"},{"type":"text","text":"and interests)"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：patri（父亲）+ot→把祖国当父亲看待的人→爱国者"},{"type":"text","text":"patriotic (adj. 爱国的)"},{"type":"entry","text":"nimble","headword":"nimble"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 敏捷的，灵活的(moving quickly and lightly)"},{"type":"text","text":"['nzmbl]"},{"type":"note","text":"图联想记忆：偷窃（nim）需要手脚灵活（nimble）"},{"type":"text","text":"图nimbleness（n.灵活：敏捷）"},{"type":"entry","text":"stoic","headword":"stoic"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.坚忍克己之人(a person firmly restraining response to pain or distress)"},{"type":"text","text":"['staurk]"},{"type":"text","text":"图来自希腊哲学流派Stoic（斯多葛学派），主张坚忍克己"},{"type":"text","text":"stoicism（n.对痛苦的默默承受或泰然处之：坚忍）"},{"type":"entry","text":"glutinous","headword":"glutinous"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.黏的，胶状的（gluey.sticky)"},{"type":"text","text":"['glu:tanas]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自glue（n.胶，胶水）"},{"type":"text","text":"gluten（n.面筋；谷蛋白）"},{"type":"entry","text":"provincial","headword":"provincial"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj省的，地方的：偏狭的，粗俗的（limitedin outlook)"},{"type":"text","text":"[pra'vinJ]"},{"type":"text","text":"图来自province（n.省）"},{"type":"text","text":"This poetry is not provincial; it is more likely to appeal to an international"},{"type":"text","text":"audience than is poetry with strictly regional themes."},{"type":"text","text":"agrestic, bucolic, countrified, rustic"},{"type":"text","text":"provincialism（n.胸襟狭隧，排外主义）"},{"type":"entry","text":"pharmacology","headword":"pharmacology"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.药理学，药物学：药理"},{"type":"text","text":"[fa:rma'ka:lad3i]"},{"type":"text","text":"pharmacologically（n.药理学；药理方面）"},{"type":"entry","text":"superannuate","headword":"superannuate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 使退休领养老金(to retire and pension because of age or infirmity)"},{"type":"text","text":"[su:par'anjuert]"},{"type":"text","text":"superannuation（n.退休金，养老金）"},{"type":"entry","text":"extricate","headword":"extricate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.摆脱，脱离：拯救，救出（to set free;release）"},{"type":"text","text":"['ekstrikert]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：ex（向外）+tric（小障碍物）+ate→从小障碍物中出来→敦出"}]},{"number":249,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<< GRE词汇精选乱L序版"},{"type":"entry","text":"narcissist","headword":"narcissist"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 自恋狂, 自恋者(a person who has abnormal and excessive love or admiration"},{"type":"text","text":"[na:r'sisist]"},{"type":"text","text":"for oneself)"},{"type":"text","text":"narcissistic（adj自恋的：自我欣赏的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"ostensible","headword":"ostensible"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj表面上的（apparent, seeming. professed)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a:'stensabl]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：ostens（出现）+ible→出现的→表面上的"},{"type":"text","text":"ostensibly (adv 表面上);ostentatiousness (n.外表)"},{"type":"entry","text":"vituperate","headword":"vituperate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 漫骂，导骂(to abuse or censure severely or abusively)"},{"type":"text","text":"[var'tu:parert]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：vituper（责备）+ate→漫骂，辱骂"},{"type":"text","text":"vituperation（n.辱骂；责骂）"},{"type":"entry","text":"spasmodic","headword":"spasmodic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj整挛的(of a spasm)：间歇性的(intermittent)"},{"type":"text","text":"[spaez'ma:drk]"},{"type":"text","text":"图 spasmodic fighting 零星的战斗"},{"type":"text","text":"sporadically（acv.零星；偶发地）"},{"type":"entry","text":"pertinacious","headword":"pertinacious"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.固执的，坚决的(stubbornly or perversely persistent);坚持的(holding"},{"type":"text","text":"[p3:rtn'erfas]"},{"type":"text","text":"tenaciously to a purpose belief, opinion, or course of action)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：per（始终）+tin（拿住）+acious→始终拿住不放→固执的"},{"type":"text","text":"pertinacity (n.固执)"},{"type":"entry","text":"retract","headword":"retract"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 撤回，取消(to take back or withdraw);缩回，拉回(to draw or pull back)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rr'traekt]"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：re（反）+tract（拉）→拉回去→拉回"},{"type":"text","text":"retraction（n.拉回；撒销）"},{"type":"entry","text":"sycophant","headword":"sycophant"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 马屁精(a servile self-seeking flatterer)"},{"type":"text","text":"['srkafaent]"},{"type":"text","text":"圈词根记忆：syco（无花果）+phan（显现）+t→献上无花果→马屁精"},{"type":"text","text":"sycophancy（n.阿奉承，溜须拍马）"},{"type":"entry","text":"venerate","headword":"venerate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.崇敬，敬仰(to regard with reverential respect)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：vener（尊敬）+ate→崇敬"},{"type":"text","text":"['venarert]"},{"type":"text","text":"adore, revere, worship"},{"type":"text","text":"veneration (n.尊敬）"},{"type":"entry","text":"proselytize","headword":"proselytize"},{"type":"text","text":"(使)依(to recruit or convert to a new faith)"},{"type":"text","text":"['pra:salatarz]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：pros（靠近）+elyt（来到）+ize→走到（佛祖）面前→（使）板依"},{"type":"text","text":"proselytizer（n.说客）"},{"type":"entry","text":"vivacious","headword":"vivacious"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj活泼的，有生气的，快活的(lively in temper, conduct, or spirit; sprightly)"},{"type":"text","text":"[vr'verfas]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：viv（生命）+acious（多·的）→多生命的→活泼的"},{"type":"text","text":"vivacity（n.活力：魅力：生气）"},{"type":"entry","text":"reminisce","headword":"reminisce"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 追忆,[回]想(to indulge in reminiscence)"},{"type":"text","text":"[remx'nrs]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：re（重新）+min（看作mind，思维）+isce→重新回到思维中→追忆"},{"type":"text","text":"图reminiscence（n.回忆：回忆录）"}]},{"number":250,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 20 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"flag","headword":"flag"},{"type":"definition","text":"v减弱，衰退（to lose strength)：枯要（to droop)"},{"type":"text","text":"[flaeg]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：flag作名词意为“旗，国旗”→当运动员体力衰退时，啦啦队摇旗呐"},{"type":"text","text":"喊为他们鼓劲"},{"type":"text","text":"deteriorate, languish, wilt"},{"type":"text","text":"图unflagging （adj.不倦的：蓬勃的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"unflappable","headword":"unflappable"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 不惊慌的，镇定的(marked by assurance and self-control)"},{"type":"text","text":"[An'flaepabl]"},{"type":"text","text":"composed, imperturbable, self-possessed, unrufled"},{"type":"text","text":"图unflappability (n.镇定）"},{"type":"entry","text":"airtight","headword":"airtight"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 密闭的，不透气的(too tight for air or gas to enter or escape)"},{"type":"text","text":"['ertart]"},{"type":"text","text":"圆组合词：air（空气）+tight（紧的，不透气的）→密闭的，不透气的"},{"type":"text","text":"watertight（adj 不透水的，防水的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"combustible","headword":"combustible"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.易燃的(flammable);易激动的(easily aroused)"},{"type":"text","text":"[kam'bAstabl]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：com（强调）+bust（燃烧）+ible→易燃的"},{"type":"entry","text":"lambaste","headword":"lambaste"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 痛打(to beat soundlly); 痛骂(to scold or denounce severely)"},{"type":"text","text":"[laem'berst]"},{"type":"text","text":"国组合词：lam（鞭打）+baste（棒打)→痛打"},{"type":"text","text":"denounce, deride"},{"type":"entry","text":"gaffe","headword":"gaffe"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.（社交上令人不快的）失礼，失态（a social or diplomatic blunder)"},{"type":"text","text":"[gaef]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆联想记忆：gaff（鱼叉）+e→像用鱼叉刺人→失言，失态"}]}]}